Dialogue: 8,0:17:44.89,0:17:48.82,P-可胖,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}はい みんなでナンバーワンワンワン
Dialogue: 8,0:17:49.87,0:17:52.59,F-julia,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}でも本当にうちら大丈夫かなぁ
Dialogue: 8,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.14,A-丽花,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}大丈夫
Dialogue: 8,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.40,A-丽花,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}一人一人が輝いていれば
Dialogue: 8,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.68,A-丽花,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}その色が混ざりあって
Dialogue: 8,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.90,A-丽花,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}私たちの色になりますから
Dialogue: 8,0:18:04.92,0:18:06.15,F-步,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}そっか
Dialogue: 8,0:18:06.92,0:18:08.94,F-步,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}もしかしてプロデューサーも
Dialogue: 8,0:18:15.91,0:18:19.34,P-可胖,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}本当に 自由に羽ばたいているみたいでしたねー
Dialogue: 8,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.86,A-丽花,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}うん どこまでも広がる大きな空を
Dialogue: 8,0:18:23.08,0:18:27.50,F-步,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}うん 歌織さんにも紬にも みんなに感謝だよ
Dialogue: 8,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.72,F-julia,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}それじゃあ 続こうか
Dialogue: 8,0:18:31.63,0:18:34.77,F-julia,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}うちらの翼で 思いっきり羽ばたこう！
