Dialogue: 8,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.77,P-emily,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}そして皆さんがつないでくれた
Dialogue: 8,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.38,A-日向,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}私たちも頑張るよ
Dialogue: 8,0:19:11.66,0:19:13.33,F-步,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}それぞれの輝きで
Dialogue: 8,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.54,F-昴,,0,0,20,,{\fnFOT-TsukuGo Pro E\fs60\bord2.5}このライブを最後まで
